author: Alexandra Berzon
title: Planes Full of Women Head to Anti-Trump Protest - Washington Wire - WSJ
text:
For many women angered by Donald Trump becoming president, the best place to be Friday was in the air. As Mr. Trump was being sworn in as president on the west face of the Capitol, women on flights to the nation’s capital for a Saturday protest rally hooted, clapped and celebrated together, enjoying some spontaneous […]
